To build and install kandau you will need at least CMake 2.6

1 Type `cmake CMakeLists.txt'. If you want install kandau in a custom path,
just add -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX before CMAkeLists.txt.
Example:
`cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr CMakeLists.txt'

2 Type `make' to compile the package.
3 Type `make install' to install the library.

For more information please visit:
http://www.cmake.org/HTML/Documentation.html
